menu "CANopenNode Stack Config"

    config CO_MULTIPLE_OD
        bool "Enable MULTIPLE_OD"
        default false
        help
            Enable CANopenNode support for multiple Object Dictionaries.
            When enabled, CANopen parameters are provided through CO_config_t
            at CO_new() time. When disabled, CANopenNode uses the default
            OD.h definitions directly, which lowers memory consumption and
            startup time.

endmenu
